{"word":"H3841 - לִבְנָה - Libnâh - lib-naw' - Libnah","slug":"H3841","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">לִבְנָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Libnâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>lib-naw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Libnah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>לבנה</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>libnâh</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>lib-naw'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Libnah = \"pavement\" <ol><li>a royal city of the Canaanites in the southwest captured by Joshua; allocated to Judah and made a Levitical city; site unknown</li><li>a station between Sinai and Kadesh of Israel during their wilderness wanderings</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H3839\">H3839</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3828\">H3828</a>, <a href=\"#/H3829\">H3829</a>, <a href=\"#/H3835\">H3835</a>, <a href=\"#/H3836\">H3836</a>, <a href=\"#/H3837\">H3837</a>, <a href=\"#/H3838\">H3838</a>, <a href=\"#/H3839\">H3839</a>, <a href=\"#/H3840\">H3840</a>, <a href=\"#/H3842\">H3842</a>, <a href=\"#/H3843\">H3843</a>, <a href=\"#/H3844\">H3844</a>, <a href=\"#/H3845\">H3845</a>, <a href=\"#/H3846\">H3846</a>, <a href=\"#/H4192\">H4192</a>, <a href=\"#/H4404\">H4404</a>"}]}